    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252240/extras/786aed78ec2ac167602e28346ac2c1f7.poster.avif?t=1749740747\" width=800 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252240/extras/786aed78ec2ac167602e28346ac2c1f7.webm?t=1749740747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252240/extras/786aed78ec2ac167602e28346ac2c1f7.mp4?t=1749740747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mircea</strong> is a short spooky adventure that takes place in the subway system.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The underground tunnels that connect the city have been infested by mysterious, bug-like beings, and the station manager has been tasked with fixing the problem. To cut costs, the station manager decided to task his daughter, Abi, with exploring the subway, investigating and understanding the monsters to capture them...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>...before they capture her.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your way through the complex interconnected tunnels of the city's underground subway in this classic survival horror inspired adventure game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter an eclectic assortment of characters that each have their own reasons and motives for being in the subway past closing hours.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather items, analyze clues and solve puzzles to capture the mysterious beings... but are they really a pest?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:/